<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN"
  "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="zh-CN" lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="application/xhtml+xml; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Agent Framework Scratch — 手写 Agent 框架</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
      :root {
        --bg: #f6f7f9;
        --surface: #ffffff;
        --border: #e8eaee;
        --text: #1a1d23;
        --muted: #5c6370;
        --accent: #2563eb;
        --accent-soft: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
        --sidebar-w: 240px;
        --radius: 10px;
        --shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background: var(--bg);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
      a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

      /* 隐藏 checkbox，用 label 触发 */
      #sidebar-toggle {
        position: absolute;
        width: 1px;
        height: 1px;
        padding: 0;
        margin: -1px;
        overflow: hidden;
        clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
        border: 0;
      }

      .app {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      /* —— 侧栏 —— */
      .sidebar {
        position: fixed;
        left: 0;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        width: var(--sidebar-w);
        z-index: 20;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        background: var(--surface);
        border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        transform: translateX(0);
        transition: transform 0.22s ease;
      }
      .sidebar-brand {
        padding: 1.15rem 1.1rem 0.85rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }
      .sidebar-brand strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 650;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        color: var(--text);
      }
      .sidebar-brand span {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 0.2rem;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-weight: 400;
      }
      .nav-scroll {
        flex: 1;
        overflow-y: auto;
        padding: 0.65rem 0.5rem 1rem;
      }
      .nav-label {
        margin: 0.75rem 0.55rem 0.35rem;
        font-size: 0.68rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #94a3b8;
      }
      .nav-list {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .nav-list li { margin: 0; }
      .nav-list a {
        display: block;
        padding: 0.45rem 0.65rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: #334155;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background 0.12s ease, color 0.12s ease;
      }
      .nav-list a:hover {
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      /* —— 主区 —— */
      .main {
        flex: 1;
        margin-left: var(--sidebar-w);
        min-width: 0;
        transition: margin-left 0.22s ease;
      }
      .topbar {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 10;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.65rem;
        padding: 0.65rem 1.1rem;
        background: rgba(246, 247, 249, 0.85);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }
      .btn-sidebar {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 2.25rem;
        height: 2.25rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--surface);
        cursor: pointer;
        color: var(--text);
        flex-shrink: 0;
        transition: background 0.12s ease, border-color 0.12s ease;
      }
      .btn-sidebar:hover {
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        border-color: #bfdbfe;
      }
      .btn-sidebar svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }
      .topbar-title {
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #0f172a;
        white-space: nowrap;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-overflow: ellipsis;
      }

      .content {
        max-width: 820px;
        padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem 3rem;
      }
      .hero {
        padding: 1.35rem 1.25rem;
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }
      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 3.4vw, 1.75rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        color: #0f172a;
      }
      .tagline {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.98rem;
      }
      .badges {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #475569;
        background: #f1f5f9;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }
      .lead { margin: 0; color: #334155; font-size: 0.95rem; }

      section { margin-top: 2rem; }
      section h2 {
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        font-weight: 650;
        color: #0f172a;
        padding-bottom: 0.45rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }
      section p { margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #334155; font-size: 0.94rem; }
      section ul {
        margin: 0.4rem 0 0;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
        color: #334155;
        font-size: 0.94rem;
      }
      section li { margin: 0.35rem 0; }
      .note {
        margin-top: 1.25rem;
        padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: #475569;
      }
      code {
        font-family: ui-monospace, Consolas, "Cascadia Code", monospace;
        font-size: 0.86em;
        padding: 0.12em 0.35em;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background: #f1f5f9;
        color: #0f172a;
      }

      /* 窄屏遮罩：侧栏打开时点击主区域外收起（不影响桌面端正文点击） */
      .main-backdrop {
        display: none;
      }

      /* 收起侧栏 */
      #sidebar-toggle:checked ~ .app .sidebar {
        transform: translateX(-100%);
      }
      #sidebar-toggle:checked ~ .app .main {
        margin-left: 0;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .sidebar {
          box-shadow: 8px 0 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
          z-index: 40;
        }
        .topbar { z-index: 30; position: relative; }
        .main { margin-left: 0 !important; }
        #sidebar-toggle:not(:checked) ~ .app .main-backdrop {
          display: block;
          position: fixed;
          z-index: 12;
          top: 0;
          right: 0;
          bottom: 0;
          left: 0;
          cursor: pointer;
          background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
        }
        #sidebar-toggle:checked ~ .app .main-backdrop {
          display: none;
        }
      }

      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        .sidebar,
        .main {
          transition: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <input type="checkbox" id="sidebar-toggle" />
    <div class="app">
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-brand">
          <strong>Agent Framework</strong>
          <span>Scratch · 手写框架</span>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav-scroll">
          <div class="nav-label">文档</div>
          <ul class="nav-list">
            <li><a href="#home">首页</a></li>
            <li><a href="#overview">项目概述</a></li>
            <li><a href="#focus">核心能力</a></li>
            <li><a href="#why-xml">关于 index.xml</a></li>
            <li><a href="#deploy">部署与预览</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </aside>

      <div class="main">
        <label class="main-backdrop" for="sidebar-toggle">&#160;</label>
        <header class="topbar">
          <label for="sidebar-toggle" class="btn-sidebar" title="显示 / 隐藏侧栏">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
            </svg>
          </label>
          <span class="topbar-title">Agent Framework Scratch</span>
        </header>

        <div class="content">
          <section id="home">
            <div class="hero">
              <h1>Agent Framework Scratch</h1>
              <p class="tagline">手写 Agent 框架 — 从循环与工具开始，把智能体做成可读、可换、可测的代码。</p>
              <div class="badges">
                <span class="badge">hand-written</span>
                <span class="badge">中文文档</span>
                <span class="badge">GitHub Pages</span>
                <span class="badge">侧栏可隐藏</span>
              </div>
              <p class="lead">
                本仓库是一个<strong>从头实现</strong>的 Agent 实验项目：关注对话与工具调用的主循环、注册与执行隔离、以及后续可扩展的记忆与多模型适配。
                与「积木式 SDK」不同，这里优先保证<strong>你能打开文件就读懂数据流</strong>，再逐步加上工程化能力。
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="overview">
            <h2>项目概述</h2>
            <p>
              目标是把推理循环、工具调用、上下文与记忆等能力拆开实现，边界清晰，便于单测与替换。
              后续可接 CLI、HTTP 等入口；当前文档页为静态说明，代码结构将随开发在仓库中逐步完善。
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="focus">
            <h2>核心能力</h2>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Agent 主循环：</strong>思考 → 行动 → 观察，终止条件与迭代上限可控。</li>
              <li><strong>工具层：</strong>显式注册、同步/异步边界清晰，便于对接 HTTP、脚本与本地能力。</li>
              <li><strong>上下文：</strong>可插拔的压缩与摘要策略（规划中）。</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section id="why-xml">
            <h2>关于 index.xml</h2>
            <p>
              GitHub Pages 默认使用 <code>index.html</code> 作为目录首页；本仓库在 <code>docs/index.html</code> 中跳转到本页。
              你也可以<strong>直接访问</strong>路径以 <code>/index.xml</code> 结尾的 URL，作为固定的 XHTML 文档入口。
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="deploy">
            <h2>部署与预览</h2>
            <p>
              在 GitHub 仓库 <strong>Settings → Pages</strong> 中，选择从分支的 <code>/docs</code> 文件夹发布。
            </p>
            <div class="note">
              本地预览：在 <code>docs</code> 目录执行 <code>python -m http.server 8765</code>，浏览器打开
              <code>http://127.0.0.1:8765/index.xml</code>。
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
